:::Yusef/D'arbanville/Jagger:::

::The ship lands on Earth in the area that will someday be New York City. 
They walk out and look around them::
Yusef: What a strange place.
D'arbanville: Kind of scary.....
Jagger: Don't worry, love, I'll protect you!
Yusef: No I will!
::He takes out his guitar and starts singing::
Yusef: The moment that you walked inside my door,
I knew i needn't look no more
I'd seen many other girls before
But heaven must've programmed you!
::D'arbanville smiles at the sentimental words sung by Yusef, but then she 
hears Jagger::
Jagger: I wanna be your lover baby
I wanna be your man
I wanna be your lover baby
I wanna be your man!
::D'arbanville sees that she has two suitors. As a woman of few words, she 
wasn't dying to break up the fight(plus she was happy that two men were 
fighting over her). Soon they threw down their guitars and started brawling 
all out, with neither one conceding an inch::

--part1_a.12fb28cc.28deb985_boundary
